
---

## `.gitignore` (Next.js + TS + Tailwind)

```gitignore
# dependencies
node_modules/

# next
.next/
out/

# production
build/

# env files
.env
.env.*.local
.env.local

# logs
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
*.log

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo

# TypeScript
*.tsbuildinfo

# Turbopack / cache
.turbo/
.cache/

# coverage
coverage/

# misc
.vercel/

